            <p class="egenie-strapline"><span class="egenie"><em>e</em>genie</span> - Making Home Appliances and Televisions Affordable</p>
            <h1><span class="egenie"><em>e</em>genie</span> - FAQs</h1>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What's included in the weekly price?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
                <p>
                Our weekly price includes installation and demonstration of the home appliance or television and full service support for the life of the agreement. The best part is there is no worry of unexpected repair bills.
                </p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs icon-toggle-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>How do I complete an application?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
                <p>
                We like to make it easy to apply, you can apply online either from you mobile or computer and we will call you back to let you know how your application is proceeding or for further information. If you prefer you can call us on 0345 0702337.
                </p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs icon-toggle-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Do you credit check my application?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
                <p>
                Yes - we perform a credit check on all applications to assess suitability. Sometimes due to the credit score, we may not always be able to offer the product of your choice. If this is the case, we may offer a more suitable alternative or your application may have to be declined.
                </p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs icon-toggle-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Do I need to give a reference for renting with egenie?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
                <p>
                A reference is not required but we do ask for two points of contact. This can be a family member not living at the same address. This is in case we lose touch with you.
                </p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What ID do I need to show?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>When we deliver the products you will need to show ID that will verify your identity.</p> 
               <p><strong>You will be required to show two of the following:</strong></p>
               <ul>
                <li>Passport</li>
                  <li>UK driving licence</li>
                  <li>Credit card &amp; credit card statement</li>
                  <li>Cheque/debit card and statement</li>
                  <li>DWP benefit letter and Post Office card</li>
                  <li>Bank statements for 2 months</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>You will also need to show one of the following:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Council tax bill for the current tax year</li>
                  <li>Two utility bills, e.g. gas, electric, water etc</li>
                </ul>
                </div>
               </aside>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What will I have to pay on delivery?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>On delivery you will be required to pay the first weekly payment and a &pound;15 administration charge.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Why has the type of product changed from what I applied for?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>When we take your application you are asked for permission to perform a credit check. Depending on the credit score we may not be able to offer the product of your choice. Where applicable, we may offer a more affordable alternative (for example a quality refurbished product), or in some cases we may have to decline your application.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>How long is the agreement?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Our rental agreements are 12 months for our quality refurbished product or  18 months for new equipment.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Do I have to be there for delivery?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Yes - the applicant will be required to be at the home address to sign the agreement, show the required ID and pay the first weekly payment and administration fee.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>

              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Do you offer timed deliveries?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>We offer an SMS text service where you will receive a text notification the evening before delivery, indicating an estimated time slot for your delivery.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>              


               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Will you install and demonstrate the equipment?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Yes -as part of your <span class="egenie"><em>e</em>genie</span> rental agreement we will install the equipment into the room of your choice and demonstrate the functions of the product and give user training. </p>
              <p>If you have chosen a washing machine we will plumb this in to your existing services. you will need to have a waste outlet, cold water feed pipe and fixed electrical socket within 1.5 metres of the appliance. Once installed, we will power on the washing machine and draw in the water and then pump it out to test the machine. Our Installation team will then demonstrate the user functions of the appliance.</p>
              <p>If you have chosen one of our televisions, or home cinema systems, our Installation team will unpack and install the equipment into the room of your choice. Once installed, they will tune in the channels and sort into the order of your choice. They will then demonstrate the features of the television.</p>
              <p>If you have chosen a Smart television you will require broadband with a recommended 3mb/s for streaming content like BBC iPlayer or Netflix.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Will you connect up my games console, set top box or DVD?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Yes, connecting up your devices is all part of the service - the only provision is that non generic leads, such as a games console leads, are provided to our installer.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Will you take away my old washing machine?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>We can take your old washing machine away but there is a handling charge of &pound;10.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What times are you open?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Online applications via our website can be made from your computer or mobile device 27/7.</p>
                <p>If you would like to speak to our experienced sales team they are available between 09:00 and 19:00 Monday to Friday and 08:30 to 16:30 on Saturdays.  Telephone 01737 647200.</p>
                <p>Our customer service team who will handle your general enquires and repairs are available between 08:00 and 18:00 Monday to Friday and  08:00 to 16:30 on Saturdays. Telephone 0345 0702337.</p>
                <p>If you wish to make a payment or discuss your payment method our accounts team are available between 09:00 and 17:30 Monday to Friday and 08:00 to 16:30 on Saturdays. Telephone 01737 647500.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What is Quality refurbished product?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>We realise that not all budgets can stretch to new products so we offer affordable quality refurbished home appliances and televisions, from the great brand names that consumers know and expect.  All of our quality refurbished range has undergone a full service and been thoroughly examined by our own expert engineers.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Is service included in the weekly price?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Yes - with our weekly payment rental agreement we offer fully inclusive installation, comprehensive demonstration and no repair bills for the life of the agreement on all our home appliances, television and home cinema systems.</p>
            <p>Our nationwide network of service centres and our own professional field service engineers and installation teams deliver a premium service with a same day breakdown response should anything go wrong.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
               <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Who do I phone or email if I have a problem with my equipment?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Please call our Customer Service team on 0345 0702340 or email <a href="mailto:repairs@egenie.co.uk">repairs@egenie.co.uk</a></p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>Is there a call out charge for repairs?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>No, a key benefit of our rental agreements is that you will never have to pay for any repair bills.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>If I call you out and it is not a fault is there a call a charge?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>No, as a customer of <span class="egenie"><em>e</em>genie</span> we will not charge for non-fault call outs.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
              <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>If I just need advice on my rental equipment who do I call?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>We offer free inclusive advice and have a technical support team who can help you with all types of questions from ‘How do I set up recording on my recorder?’ or ‘How do I watch BBCiplayer on my smart television?’ to ‘Why is my washing machine bleeping when it finishes a wash?’</p>
               <p>Please call 0345 0702341 where our team will be happy to offer any technical advice.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>I would like to update my equipment, what do I do?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>At <span class="egenie"><em>e</em>genie</span>, we realise that technology is forever evolving. Technological advances make newer products more efficient or cheaper to run, or more impressive aesthetically. If you have reached the minimum term of your rental agreement you can apply to update your equipment.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>I am experiencing financial or other difficulties what should I do?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>Please contact us as soon as possible if you are experiencing financial or other difficulties that might result in your account falling into arrears.</p>
              <p>We want to help you where we can and our accounts team can be reached on 0345 6715715</p>
              </div>
              </aside>
             <aside class="toggler-faqs">
              <h3 class="toggle-link-faqs"><span class="icon-toggle"></span>What do I do if I wish to terminate my agreement?</h3>
              <div class="toggle-box-faqs">
               <p>If you wish to terminate your agreement and it has reached at least the minimum term you must give us at least one month’s written notice. Please send your notice letter to 7 Wells Place, Redhill, Surrey, RH1 3DR or email <a href="mailto:cancellations@egenie.co.uk">cancellations@egenie.co.uk</a>.</p>
              </div>
              </aside>

